query:
SELECT po.id, po.orderNumber, po.customerOrderNumber,
       poi.id as itemId, poi.productId, p.sku, poi.requestedQuantity
FROM pickingOrders po
LEFT JOIN pickingOrderItems poi ON po.id = poi.pickingOrderId
LEFT JOIN products p ON poi.productId = p.id
WHERE po.status = 'picked'
ORDER BY po.id DESC
LIMIT 15;
